{"tid":2359310,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發！」型月創辦人奈須磨菇被發現在家身中多刀，當場身亡，遊戲「魔法使之夜2」恐遙遙無期","createTime":"2021-01-08T20:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T06:25:11.000Z","uid":231600,"like":5,"dislike":143,"uniUserReply":24,"remark":"[gold]⚠️ 管理團隊警示：本主題內容已被回報為「真實性有待確定，及可能含有虛假資訊」，請各位留意。[/gold]\n警示措施說明：https://lih.kg/eobQbT","replies":[{"pid":"98dbe31e4e1d7e9f4e28bd5ebfe51656f0582378","tid":2359310,"uid":231600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T20:04:03.000Z","msg":"日本知名團體Type Moon，因作品fate zero而廣為人知，更衍生出其後續作品fate stay night UBW的重製。曾在2014年10月被動畫化。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dz7YvFD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdz7YvFD.jpg&h=d82ed127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而於2015年7月，日本人氣手機遊戲「Fate Grand Order」推出後更風扉全球，常年成為遊戲界課金排行榜首。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJEoGOd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJEoGOd.png&h=9a91c528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而令小小的一個團體發揚光大的正是創辦人，奈須磨菇。他曾制作出「月姫」、「空之境界」等高人氣作品。但可惜天意弄人，於2021年1月6日在自家大宅被發現身中29刀，救護人員到達現場後已返魂乏術。恐怕其手下的「魔法使之夜2」也難以再開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有網友亦留言說：「都是因為你把fate當搖錢樹才會被攻擊。」其後，此留言已被迅速刪除"},{"pid":"05170720bec377af0f6b7f8729222648eea6db7f","tid":2359310,"uid":231600,"like":4,"dislike":59,"score":-55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T20:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E9f7o4x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE9f7o4x.jpg&h=faf219f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有救護人員在現場把死者相片上傳到網上，其後圖片已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f77fe3a43a209f19d66f8127be60d2af0a3ed04","tid":2359310,"uid":45120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T20:10:18.000Z","msg":"抽極都冇 俾我都劈"},{"pid":"7fc847f98764391a9b8f39c3d4a01fcfb30a18ea","tid":2359310,"uid":231600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f77fe3a43a209f19d66f8127be60d2af0a3ed04","tid":2359310,"uid":45120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T20:10:18.000Z","msg":"抽極都